title: FREMONT COUNTY BOUNDRY [1:24,000-scale]
name: FREMONT COUNTY BOUNDRY [1:24,000-scale]
description: This data set portrays the county boundaries of Idaho as of 2003. The data set was created by digitizing county polygon features from 1:24,000-scale Digital Raster Graphic (DRG) files produced by the U.S. Geological Survey.
